\fB\-W\fP[\fIFMT\fP]\fB, \-W\fP[=\fIFMT\fP]\fB, \-\-write\-index\fP[=\fIFMT\fP]
.RS 4
Automatically index the output file.  \fIFMT\fP is optional and can be
