biallelic sites into multiallelic records (\fB+\fP). An optional type string
can follow which controls variant types which should be split or merged
together: If only SNP records should be split or merged, specify \fIsnps\fP; if
both SNPs and indels should be merged separately into two records, specify
\fIboth\fP; if SNPs and indels should be merged into a single record, specify
\fIany\fP.
\~
